To install, please run these commands:
mkdir build
cd build 
cmake ..
make install

Build dependencies (for a Ubuntu system, please refer to your distribution naming scheme for equivalent):
 valac,
 libappindicator-dev,
 libgee-dev,
 libnotify-dev,
 libgtk2.0-dev,
 libgtk-3-dev,
 intltool,
 pkg-config,
 cmake
